headline: How the Story Around Jack Henry Has Shifted After Recent Analyst and Market Updates
summary: Jack Henry & Associates' fair value estimate has seen a slight decrease, moving from $183.18 to $181.55, with the discount rate nudging up just marginally. This modest adjustment reflects both recent strengths and emerging risks highlighted by analysts following the company's latest performance.
